    "data": [
        {
            "title": "若能源價格未回落 歐洲央行官員料6月加息",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 知情人士稱，除非能源價格和結束伊朗戰爭方面出現積極進展，否則<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"歐洲央行\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:歐洲央行;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/歐洲央行\">歐洲央行</a>決策者很可能在6月下次會議上加息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">因談及非公開討論而不願具名的知情人士表示，如果衝突持續，避免加息的可能性將非常小。不過他們強調，尚未作出任何決定，形勢也可能會迅速改變。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲央行發言人拒絕置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲央行總裁拉加德早些時候示意，在周四會議上決策者曾討論但最終否決了加息方案，不過央行將在6月會議上考慮加息可能性。官員們將在下次會議上獲得最新預測，經濟學家和投資者預計他們屆時將選擇加息25個基點。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-bb756928-3702-3a02-b62f-affcdc9de744-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">拉加德表示，接下來的六周將是評估經濟形勢的合適時機，以便基於經過驗證和重新審視的信息作出審慎決策。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：歐洲央行維持利率不變 拉加德傳遞或在6月考慮加息的信號</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"歐洲央行總裁克里斯蒂娜·拉加德來源： 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/T.qRLI8fOK3TPp66wTqByg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/df7daaf8827d040e40d8eee89f12f6d6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">歐洲央行總裁克里斯蒂娜·拉加德來源： 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">到目前為止，儘管整體通膨率已跳升至3%，但石油和天然氣成本的飆升尚未引發所謂的第二輪效應，因此官員們尚未確信有必要收緊貨幣政策。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：歐元區經濟成長意外放緩 伊朗戰爭加劇滯脹風險</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博经济研究表示：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">“欧洲央行正面临严峻的两难困境，能源冲击导致通胀跃升而经济下滑。拉加德在新闻发布会上提到曾讨论加息，基调更趋鹰派。总体而言，尽管欧洲央行可能在6月加息，但其前景较金融市场预期更为鸽派，今年不太可能激进收紧政策。”</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—彭博经济学家David Powell和Simona Delle Chiaie。点击此处查看全文</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場並不認為歐洲央行會在6月止步，當前定價顯示年底前將累計加息三次。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題ECB Officials See June Hike If Energy Prices Don’t Ease First</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Jana Randow、Alexander Weber.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%A5%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E6%9C%AA%E5%9B%9E%E8%90%BD-%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E6%96%996%E6%9C%88%E5%8A%A0%E6%81%AF-153741185.html",
